Uses of Class
edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.device.Tile

Packages that use Tile
edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.design The design package has all the classes necessary to represent XDL designs in RapidSmith. 
edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.device The device package represents all of the resources available on an FPGA device (part name, tiles, primitive sites and routing resources). 
edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.router The router package will have a full design router, but it is still under construction at the moment.
